Cute Dress! An easy fit waistless shift dress with jumbo pockets - handy!!

These dresses are all lovingly handmade in my home studio from recycled and vintage fabrics.  To choose your fabric go to <a href="http://rummagestyle.blogspot.com.au/p/fabrics.html" class="external">View Fabric</a> and send me a message with your choice.  You can email me here theresa@rummagestyle.com or just leave a message when you pay with Paypal.

*Please note that the fabric in the photo has been sold.

**Often there is only enough of any given fabric to make one garment.  In the event of two people ordering the same fabric in a short period of time then it will be a first in best dressed policy.


Sizing;
Please note - if you need help with measurements just ask and If your size isn't there don't worry, I'll cut a pattern to your measurements!


